nx.description: The shared object has NX bit set. This marks a memory page non-executable making attacker injected shellcode non-executable.

stack_canary.description: This shared object has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has full RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In Full RELRO, the entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) is marked as read-only.

runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

playstore_details.title: Crypto Tracker and Portfolio - Coin Market Info
playstore_details.description:
Coin Market Info enables you quick and easy access to Cryptocurrency prices, market cap, exchange markets, coin details more on over 1400 Cryptocurrency including Bitcoin, Etherium, Iota, Ripple & many more.

📋 Cryptocurrency Portfolio!
Just enter the number of coins you have from each Cryptocurrency and see how much they all worth.

📰 Crypto News! Get updated with the latest news from the top websites on the web! Including CoinTelegraph, CoinDesk, CCN and more!

📄 ICO - Initial Coin Offering
Track ICO's!
Live, Upcoming and Finished ICO data!
Get all the information you need about ICO's with links to the ICO's whitepaper and full information!

🔔 Price alerts
Set price alert for every coin you like and get notified once the coin reaches that value

🔝 Top and Bottom!
See which coins made the most positive and negative change in 1 hour, 24 hours or 7 days!

🕹 App Features:
★ 🔬 Track nearly all virtual currencies or ALTcoins - not only BTC (Bitcoin).
★ 📋 Portfolio Overview: View all your Cryptocurrency investments at once, and find detailed information on each coin.
★ 🔔 Price change alerts for any coin you like.
★ 💸 List of exchanges for each coin so you can see where the coin is being traded and in which value.
★ ⭐️ Favorite Cryptocurrency! Pick which ones are most important to you and star them for instant checking.
★ 🔍 Search in ALTcoins (Cryptocurrency) list from 1000+ altcoins.
★ Available for free and is dedicated to all crypto lovers.


Next features:
- ⛏ Mining tools
